tasks.description:
For each service task definition, add a logConfiguration block under the container definition:
```
"logConfiguration": {
  "logDriver": "awslogs",
  "options": {
    "awslogs-group": "/loanflow/{env}/{service-name}",
    "awslogs-region": "${AWS_REGION}",
    "awslogs-stream-prefix": "{service-name}",
    "awslogs-create-group": "true"
  }
}
```
Register new task definition revisions for all six services after the update. The awslogs-create-group option is set to true as a safety net only; the log groups are expected to already exist from the pre-creation step.
